# Mock-only Dash UI (static data, no metrics APIs or Redis).
# Local: copy to .env — optional auth Postgres via docker-compose.mock.yml (see repo root).
# Kubernetes: see k8s-mock/ (StatefulSet auth-db + 00-auth-secrets-reference.yaml) and docs/KUBERNETES_SETUP.md §3.
# Or use: scripts/run_mock.ps1 / scripts/run_mock.sh

APP_MODE=mock

# Optional: shown in sidebar and browser tab (default if unset: Datalake WebUI)
# APP_BRAND_TITLE=Datalake WebUI

# Optional: build/revision label (bottom-right in UI)
# APP_BUILD_ID=dev
